
Ranger Help for: glevels
========================

SUMMARY:    
Rangers earn Ranger XP through battle and advance automatically through
guild levels 1 to 15. Guild levels cannot exceed the limits imposed by game
level and other guild training. Ranger XP remains banked while advancement
is blocked. Each guild level grants slots, which are the only currency used
to learn Ranger skills.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: stats
